The paper deals with automated theorem proving in geometry, which is a topic that falls under the category of logic (cs.LO). Additionally, the use of a theorem prover involves artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI). The methodology for preparing and checking input files involves data structures (cs.DS) and the use of subformula strategy involves mathematical software (cs.MS). Finally, the topic of geometry and proofs could also fall under the category of computational geometry (cs.CG).
